    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelType\"><strong>Requirements</strong></span></p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl02_LabelType\">Any animal can be a clever mount.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl02_LabelType\">This mount can learn four tricks per point of Intelligence, instead of the typical three. Commanding the mount with the Handle an Animal use of the Handle Animal skill requires a successful DC 15 skill check instead of the usual DC 10, however, as it is willful and easily bored.</span></p>",
